Cc: Will Deacon <will@kernel.org>
Cc: Catalin Marinas <catalin.marinas@arm.com>
Reviewed-by: Ada Couprie Diaz <ada.coupriediaz@arm.com>
Reviewed-by: Linus Walleij <linusw@kernel.org>
